    <briefdescription>
<para>This class is able to generalize task specific trajectories from previous examples. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This method works well on tasks, where the sample trajectories are similar in shape. Therefore, several simple trajectories have to be measured and stored in files. </para>    </detaileddescription>
